Package space.sunqian.fs.object.data

Interface ObjectBuilderProvider

public interface ObjectBuilderProvider
Provider for getting ObjectBuilder.

It contains and uses a list of ObjectBuilderProvider.Handlers to sequentially attempt get the instance of ObjectBuilder. The thread safety of the methods in this interface is determined by its dependent ObjectBuilderProvider.BuilderCache. By default, they are thread-safe.

  • Method Details

    • defaultProvider

      @Nonnull static @Nonnull ObjectBuilderProvider defaultProvider()
      Returns the default ObjectBuilderProvider.

      The default ObjectBuilderProvider will cache the ObjectBuilders, which are created by its handlers, into a cache based on a ConcurrentHashMap (so it is thread-safe). And it has only one handler, which uses Invocable.of(Constructor) with the empty constructor of the target class (if it has) to implement ObjectBuilder.newBuilder() and directly returns the builder object itself on ObjectBuilder.build(Object).

      Returns:
      the default ObjectBuilderProvider
